# SeismiStats V1 Environment Variables
# =====================================
# V1 is a frontend-only application that fetches directly from USGS/PNSN APIs.
# It uses MapLibre GL JS with Carto basemaps - NO API keys required!
#
# Deployment: docker-compose.seismistats.yml
# Image: ghcr.io/dlarsen395/seismistats:latest (or :v1.x.x)
#
# This file is provided for documentation purposes only.
# V1 requires NO environment variables to run.
#
# =====================================

# No environment variables needed for V1!
# The app uses:
# - MapLibre GL JS (open source, no token required)
# - Carto basemaps (free tier, no token required)
# - USGS Earthquake API (public, no token required)
# - PNSN Tremor API (public, no token required)
#
# Simply deploy the container and it works out of the box.
